<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.10">
<l>kaṇṭacīrk kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉai</l>
<l>koṇṭacīrt toṇṭaṉ kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>paṇṭamāyp pāṭu maṭiyavark keññāṉṟum</l>
<l>aṇṭampō yāṭci yavarkka taṟintōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Servants who faithfully sing this garland of verse</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ, a devotee who attained prosperity,</l>
<l>About the lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram, with visible prosperity,</l>
<l>Having gone to heaven, [its] rule is theirs forever;</l>
<l rend="indent">we knew this was theirs!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
